{
  "stem": "13623.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I'm assigned to a detail where we had to go to the railroad station.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they had-- that camp at the time was being expanded.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they had these prefabricated barracks on the railroad cars.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We had to go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there were big, like, walls, pieces of walls.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we brought them into the camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There were other people that were assembling them, and made-- made them into a barrack.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So those walls, they assigned five or six people to carry.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Those walls had to be carried on shoulders.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So people would be supporting those walls on their shoulders.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that was our first taste of work in the camps.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had to run.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We couldn't walk.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] People were asking for water.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because it was, at that point, I would say, it was in the end of May, beginning of June.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was hot already.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They wouldn't let us drink water.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we had to run.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was a little boy of 14.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I wasn't tall enough for that thing to rest on my-- on my shoulder.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I just had to be part of this group that are carrying that piece of barrack.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we had to run.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And every time we-- we used to go out of the camp-- was a-- was a gate going out of the camp.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Whenever we went out of the camp, they would say, 50 people going out of the camp.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And whenever we came back into the camp, they would have to say the same amount of people entering the camp.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because they kept an eye on people shouldn't escape.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] On the top of the camp it had-- it had a wording in German, [NON-ENGLISH], work, makes free.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
